## 🧩 Component Guidelines

### Buttons

| Variant      | Size      | Interaction States              |
|--------------|-----------|---------------------------------|
| Default      | Small     | Colour change                   |
| Hover        | Medium    | Shadow elevation                |
| Active       | Large     | Border shift                    |
| Disabled     | –         | Reduced opacity, no interaction |

### Forms & Inputs

- **Elements** – Text fields, dropdowns, checkboxes, radio buttons  
- **Validation states** – ✅ Success · ⚠️ Warning · ❌ Error

### Reusable UI Components

| Component       | Purpose                                      |
|----------------|----------------------------------------------|
| **Cards**      | Grouped information display                  |
| **Modals**     | Overlay popups for extra details             |
| **Navbars & Tabs** | Primary user navigation                  |
| **Alerts**     | Feedback messages (success, warning, error)  |

